Essential tools include a rake, shovel, pruning shears, lawn mower, and trash bags.

Removing debris and trimming plants can improve air circulation and sunlight exposure, promoting plant health.
5 Why is proper waste disposal important in garden cleaning?
Proper disposal prevents the accumulation of rotting material, which can attract pests and harbor diseases.
